Get cell metadata from a given object

Source: R/utils-classes.R
get_colData.Rd

Get cell metadata

Usage

get_colData(object)

Arguments

object

a SingleCellExperiment object

Value

dataframe containing object metadata

Examples


data(small_example_dataset)
get_colData(small_example_dataset)
